<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins">
    <title>Event Reminder</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff !important;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #0062cc;
      }
      .center-button {
        text-align: center;
      }

    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Event Reminder!!!</h1>
      <p>Please note that your event at </p>
      <p>Subject : <%= @note.subject %></p>
      <p>Date : <%= @note.event_date %></p>

      <p>If you did not request this reminder, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>